/ Portfolio Modals
/ Use the modals below to showcase details about your portfolio projects!
/ Portfolio Modal 1
- @projects.each do |project|
  #portfolioModal.portfolio-modal.modal.fade{"aria-hidden" => "true", :role => "dialog", :tabindex => "-1", id: project.id}
    .modal-dialog
      .modal-content
        .close-modal{"data-dismiss" => "modal"}
          .lr
            .rl
        .container
          .row
            .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
              .modal-body
                / Project Details Go Here
                %h2
                  = project.title
                %p.item-intro.text-muted Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur.
                = image_tag project.image.url, class: "img-responsive img-centered"
                %p Use this area to describe your project. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Est blanditiis dolorem culpa incidunt minus dignissimos deserunt repellat aperiam quasi sunt officia expedita beatae cupiditate, maiores repudiandae, nostrum, reiciendis facere nemo!
                %p
                  %strong> Want these icons in this portfolio item sample?
                  You can download 60 of them for free, courtesy of
                  = succeed "," do
                    %a{:href => "https://getdpd.com/cart/hoplink/18076?referrer=bvbo4kax5k8ogc"} RoundIcons.com
                  = succeed "." do
                    %a{:href => "https://getdpd.com/cart/hoplink/18076?referrer=bvbo4kax5k8ogc"} here
                %ul.list-inline
                  %li Date: July 2014
                  %li Client: Round Icons
                %button.btn.btn-primary{"data-dismiss" => "modal", :type => "button"}
                  %i.fa.fa-times
                  Close Project
